 just clumsy."],[1055,1117,"I,I,"],[1117,1247,"these scissors are really sharp."],[1301,1376,"Don't worry, I'm,"],[1434,1484,"I'm, I'm fine."],[1484,1551,"That doesn't hurt."],[1618,1643,"See?"],[1735,1814,"Let's go, Robert."],[1872,2052,"She can handle a little paper cut."],[2790,2836,"I have to go."],[2969,3078,"Some bandages is in the kitchen."],[3190,3228,"Okay?"],[3411,3474,"Their shopping trip"],[3474,3624,"should keep them busy for a while."],[3757,3807,"Brian,"],[3903,4004,"I'm coming to get you."],[4550,4592,"Brian!"],[4717,4763,"Emily?"],[4829,4896,"Oh my God!"],[4925,4975,"Oh my God!"],[4975,5059,"Thank God you're ok."],[5376,5426,"Look at you."],[5714,5818,"Did Robert do this to you?"],[5826,5939,"Hey, don't worry about me."],[5939,6031,"It's not safe here."],[6039,6101,"You need to leave"],[6101,6214,"before someone finds you."],[6260,6289,"Go!"],[6318,6348,"Go!"],[6364,6414,"Go!"]],"40":[[934,971,"Nothing."],[1497,1576,"Robert has his men"],[1576,1680,"watching me around clock."],[1689,1760,"You need to leave"],[1760,1839,"before they come back."],[1839,1864,"No."],[1881,1956,"No, not without you."],[1989,2064,"If I escape,"],[2068,2177,"Robert will know it was you."],[2214,2360,"Besides, if I stay here,"],[2364,2527,"I think I can gather the proof we need"],[2527,2598,"to take him down."],[2635,2711,"Trust me on this."],[2806,2915,"Then trust me like I trust you."],[3086,3203,"Transfer your shares over to me."],[3286,3378,"Robert's gonna force you"],[3378,3445,"to give it to him."],[3511,3603,"If he succeeds,"],[3649,3791,"he will take over the family company"],[3832,3937,"and he will kill us both."],[3978,4062,"Okay, alright."],[4087,4116,"I'll do it."],[4725,4859,"Now go before they come back."]],"41":[[187,275,"Did anyone come around here"],[275,333,"while I was away?"],[354,408,"No, sir."],[487,575,"Well, that better be true."],[663,788,"Or they won't make it out of here alive."],[2097,2135,"Hold it."],[2277,2323,"Cleaning crew's"],[2323,2460,"only supposed to be in section B today."],[2540,2573,"Uh,"],[2706,2823,"unit 204 is a mess, sir."],[2844,2923,"Special request."],[4733,4842,"Well, well, well."],[4938,5117,"Caught your deaf wife sneaking off,"],[5125,5176,"didn't we?"],[5313,5501,"How's your missing brother, Emily?"]],"42":[[141,208,"Hey, sis!"],[258,346,"Where did you run off to?"],[446,529,"Did you go somewhere, honey?"],[596,784,"I was just picking up the birthday gifts"],[784,855,"you ordered, Robert."],[934,988,"Boutique had"],[988,1063,"everything arranged."],[1130,1205,"Just like you ordered."],[1776,1856,"Mr. Matthews,"],[1885,2010,"about your wife's birthday gifts-"],[2035,2097,"Jesus Christ,"],[2097,2152,"I don't give a damn"],[2156,2227,"about her stupid birthday."],[2235,2348,"Just buy her whatever."],[2385,2448,"Say it's from me."],[2781,2857,"I love my gifts."],[2865,2969,"You know exactly what I like."],[3140,3257,"This bitch is lying to us."],[3307,3428,"She went to go find her brother."],[3520,3586,"She probably heard us"],[3586,3724,"talking about the warehouse"],[3724,3832,"we're keeping him locked up in."],[4316,4358,"Stacy,"],[4400,4450,"what are you doing?"],[4479,4542,"Proving to you"],[4542,4675,"that she's not fucking deaf!"],[4850,4913,"Hey, Stacy."],[5005,5092,"Stacy, wait, wait."],[5100,5205,"Stacy, hey, hey."],[5238,5288,"Stop, stop!"],[5296,5313,"No, no,"],[5313,5426,"you, look, you don't do it."],[5426,5559,"Don't, you don't have to do it."],[5572,5663,"Stacy, stop it!"],[5663,5764,"Don't do this!"],[5789,5822,"Stop."],[5847,5926,"Stacy, Stacy!"],[5985,6018,"Fucking-"]],"43":[[679,771,"What the hell, Robert?"],[829,900,"One more second"],[900,992,"and I could've gotten rid"],[992,1109,"of your fucking wife,"],[1146,1238,"something you should've done"],[1238,1330,"a long time ago!"],[1426,1564,"Are you insane?"],[1597,1685,"We're so close to"],[1685,1755,"getting her company."],[1755,1918,"We can't kill her now."],[2502,2552,"Looks like we've been"],[2552,2631,"overthinking this."],[2681,2794,"She's definitely deaf."],[2902,3003,"Hey, Robert."],[3153,3215,"Do you think you can open"],[3215,3328,"the front doors for me?"],[3353,3440,"Hands are kinda full."],[3566,3611,"Of course,"],[3695,3728,"honey."],[3828,3895,"Be right there."],[4170,4258,"Just wait a little longer"],[4258,4337,"until I get the shares"],[4337,4391,"from her brother."],[4454,4583,"Then we can get rid of them both"],[4679,4754,"and be together."],[4817,4942,"I won't wait forever, Robert."],[5292,5447,"Believing I'm deaf was"],[5447,5584,"your first mistake."],[5634,5764,"Coming after me and my family"],[5764,5910,"will be your last."]],"44":[[312,392,"I'm gonna get those shares"],[400,479,"from Brian tonight."],[550,608,"Once I do,"],[679,855,"I'll get rid of both him and Emily"],[855,905,"for good."],[1714,1789,"Perfect."],[1839,2014,"Emily's birthday and funeral"],[2018,2152,"all in the same day."],[2218,2281,"I love it."],[3136,3190,"Sorry."],[3253,3390,"You missed your sister's birthday"],[3395,3524,"and she was so upset"],[3528,3578,"you couldn't be there"],[3578,3641,"to celebrate."],[3687,3782,"Tell me something, Robert."],[3866,3912,"The wedding,"],[3974,4062,"the family dinners,"],[4145,4279,"was it all that you steal Stewart Corp"],[4279,4362,"right from under us?"],[4412,4471,"What do you think?"],[4600,4713,"You definitely needed help."],[4754,4829,"You couldn't pulled this off"],[4829,4871,"on your own."],[5071,5142,"Was it Thomas?"]],"45":[[137,171,"Wow."],[346,467,"You definitely got some brains."],[613,713,"Smartest one in the family."],[1368,1401,"See,"],[1514,1780,"Thomas has been plotting his revenge"],[1789,1935,"since the day your parents kicked him"],[1935,2014,"out of Stewart Corp"],[2014,2139,"for embezzling millions."],[2193,2335,"He came to me with a plan"],[2335,2431,"to get rid of them"],[2477,2556,"once and for all."],[2594,2769,"And, let me tell you,"],[2932,3032,"watching that car"],[3040,3228,"go right over the cliff,"],[3520,3591,"that was something."],[3620,3707,"You son of a bitch!"],[3707,3803,"You fucking killed them!"],[3824,3920,"You fucking monster."],[3941,3970,"Yeah."],[4004,4029,"Well,"],[4029,4175,"you and Emily are gonna join them."],[4216,4308,"Unless,"],[4542,4675,"you sign over the shares to me"],[4804,4846,"right now."]],"46":[[29,162,"You sign over the shares to me"],[296,333,"right now."],[383,475,"Too late, Robert."],[487,592,"I already transferred them to Emily"],[592,667,"a long time ago."],[734,775,"What?"],[884,959,"She felt terrible"],[959,1088,"about giving those hospital shares"],[1088,1155,"over to charity,"],[1255,1393,"said she wanted to make it up to you"],[1393,1493,"and surprise you with them."],[1522,1655,"That stupid bitch."],[1710,1881,"Always ruining my plans!"],[2306,2414,"You fell for the trap,"],[2452,2565,"just like I knew you would."],[2890,2982,"And just like that,"],[3036,3211,"Emily and I have got your confession."],[3899,3941,"Robert!"],[3987,4041,"There you are."],[4104,4195,"Where did you run off to?"],[4225,4354,"I went to see your brother."],[4412,4504,"He kidnapped Brian."],[4550,4700,"Why is he telling me about him now?"],[4775,4871,"I need to be careful."],[4917,4992,"He's testing me."],[5084,5130,"Brian?"],[5205,5296,"Is, is he okay?"]],"47":[[29,133,"Oh yeah, he's fine."],[166,200,"He's fine."],[254,354,"He's staying with a friend."],[454,646,"He was too ashamed"],[658,721,"to face you"],[734,1076,"after almost ruining the family company."],[1151,1313,"He also told me about the shares"],[1322,1455,"he signed over to you."],[1522,1630,"They were supposed to be a"],[1718,1851,"surprise gift for me."],[2210,2243,"Now,"],[2302,2356,"sweetheart,"],[2594,2686,"why don't you go ahead and"],[2773,2861,"sign them over to me?"],[2969,3098,"Let me handle Stewart Corp."]],"48":[[116,196,"I just think we should follow"],[196,296,"procedure on this."],[437,521,"Hold a shareholders meeting,"],[521,579,"make it official."],[638,788,"No, that's not necessary, um,"],[788,905,"just go ahead and sign right here."],[905,1034,"We can figure all that stuff out."],[1034,1067,"Look,"],[1280,1488,"Stewart Corp is a big company."],[1589,1722,"I'm just thinking about you"],[1739,1818,"and your reputation."],[1956,2089,"This stubborn bitch!"],[2339,2385,"You're right."],[2477,2519,"You're right."],[2606,2627,"Let's do"],[2627,2731,"the shareholders' meeting."],[2882,2986,"Thank you for thinking of me."],[3103,3169,"Of course."],[3249,3374,"What kind of wife would I be if"],[3436,3486,"I didn't help you"],[3486,3553,"do it the right way?"],[3699,3791,"I'll arrange everything,"],[3849,3974,"and by next week you'll be CEO"],[3983,4074,"of Stewart Corporation."],[4646,4733,"I need to stall him,"],[4733,4859,"so Brian and I can expose"],[4859,4975,"all his evil schemes"],[4984,5071,"once and for all."],[5588,5655,"Good news."],[5689,5730,"We can have"],[5730,5818,"the shareholders' meeting"],[5818,5872,"next week."],[6001,6039,"No need."],[6097,6189,"I already spoke to Thomas,"],[6202,6322,"and he agreed we shouldn't delay it."],[6377,6443,"The meeting's been set"],[6443,6514,"for tomorrow morning."],[6673,6744,"This isn't good."],[6810,6894,"I need more time."],[6898,6990,"Why would Thomas,"],[6990,7061,"the one board member"],[7061,7148,"I trust the most,"],[7148,7219,"do this?"],[7403,7520,"Something wrong, darling?"]],"49":[[62,116,"You seem"],[225,275,"rattled."],[412,446,"Oh,"],[554,625,"no, not at all."],[784,850,"I just realized"],[850,946,"I need to stop by the office"],[946,1009,"and get something."],[1121,1259,"I'll see you later?"],[1330,1384,"Yeah."],[2248,2293,"Emily,"],[2339,2464,"I didn't expect to see you today."],[2610,2648,"Thomas,"],[2669,2752,"why did you reschedule"],[2752,2836,"the shareholder meeting?"],[2865,2994,"I had it set for next week."],[3065,3169,"I understand,"],[3240,3370,"but after your brother moved"],[3370,3528,"those emergency funds offshore,"],[3570,3653,"the board is panicking"],[3703,3832,"and they want immediate action."],[3866,3920,"I'm sorry,"],[3962,4041,"but Stewart Corp"],[4074,4258,"simply won't allow a Stewart"],[4266,4341,"to lead anymore."],[4466,4579,"Robert is your best option."]],"50":[[200,296,"Robert's signature?"],[358,487,"Even I didn't get to the hospital"],[492,550,"in time."],[604,713,"He was there to sign this"],[713,779,"when they died?"],[834,942,"And this other signature,"],[942,1088,"The, The Chancellor."],[1146,1234,"Who is this?"],[2285,2344,"Finally,"],[2448,2598,"we got rid of the Stewarts for good."],[2715,2765,"Next..."],[2827,2902,"I marry Emily,"],[2982,3086,"take everything from her."],[3728,3787,"Chancellor,"],[3866,3974,"everything's going as planned."],[4112,4158,"Good."],[4216,4300,"Keep testing Emily."],[4391,4441,"If she really"],[4441,4525,"regained her hearing,"],[4658,4729,"we need to get rid of her."],[5034,5171,"Thomas is the Chancellor."]],"51":[[196,233,"Emily,"],[296,371,"is everything alright?"],[513,571,"It was him."],[658,821,"He was behind my parents' death"],[821,955,"along with my husband."],[975,1080,"I have to be careful."],[1217,1301,"I was just thinking,"],[1334,1463,"maybe we host a banquet?"],[1555,1601,"I mean,"],[1659,1793,"we could host a grand event"],[1801,1839,"for Robert"],[1839,1951,"when he takes over tomorrow."],[1993,2018,"Oh."],[2056,2156,"And I'm sure the shareholders"],[2156,2252,"would appreciate the gesture."],[2381,2477,"I knew you'd come around."],[2769,2815,"Thomas,"],[2819,2957,"you and Robert will pay"],[2957,3053,"for what you've done."],[4266,4295,"Hey,"],[4400,4446,"clean that up."],[4600,4646,"Now."],[5359,5426,"What part of now"],[5426,5522,"don't you understand?"],[6039,6185,"Oh God, you're useless."],[6318,6352,"Here."],[6527,6606,"Make yourself useful"],[6606,6673,"and burn these."],[6740,6898,"But these belong to Ms. Stewart."],[6911,7069,"Did I stutter?"],[7152,7298,"Ms. Stewart is getting kicked"],[7298,7444,"out of Stewart Corp tomorrow,"],[7520,7653,"and her soon-to-be ex-husband"],[7653,7753,"is taking over."],[7770,7928,"So either burn these,"],[7957,8028,"or you can join her"],[8037,8120,"in the unemployment line."],[9576,9680,"Oh! Emily,"],[9751,9951,"my sweet deaf bestie."]],"52":[[200,325,"Like what I've done with the place?"],[379,450,"I see you've done"],[450,604,"some house cleaning."],[734,829,"As your stepsister,"],[829,1001,"I thought I'd take the liberty"],[1001,1101,"of clearing everything out"],[1101,1138,"for you."],[1213,1242,"You know,"],[1317,1526,"since this is Robert's office now."],[1593,1676,"Stepsister,"],[1739,1926,"I trusted you as family, Stacy."],[1926,2014,"Little did I know"],[2014,2218,"you'd sleep with my husband"],[2218,2323,"and try to kill me."],[3040,3194,"You've been such a great step-sibling,"],[3207,3265,"Stacy."],[3541,3724,"Since you enjoy cleaning so much,"],[3732,3799,"why don't I help you"],[3799,3903,"pursue your calling?"],[4175,4233,"Stewart Corp"],[4233,4400,"is hiring another janitor."],[4621,4783,"I think you'd be perfect for the job."],[4913,5005,"Are you joking?"],[5050,5171,"Robert still needs my signature"],[5171,5280,"for the banquet tomorrow."],[5572,5801,"What do you think he'd say if I told him"],[5801,5939,"you needed to be out of town"],[5939,6081,"before that happens?"],[6598,6631,"Well?"],[6777,6831,"Clean it up."],[8020,8099,"You missed a spot."],[8187,8350,"You think you've humiliated me."],[8575,8650,"Wait until I tell you"],[8650,8787,"what Robert and I have been doing"],[8796,8929,"behind your back."],[8958,8992,"No!"],[9021,9075,"Jesus!"]],"53":[[375,533,"Oh my goodness!"],[546,671,"What a disaster!"],[692,884,"Robert, you really gotta focus on"],[884,967,"where you're going."],[1067,1109,"You know what,"],[1109,1368,"why don't I grab you some towels?"],[1368,1401,"Yeah?"],[1997,2081,"Have you completely"],[2081,2160,"lost your mind?"],[2243,2394,"You were about to destroy everything"],[2427,2535,"we've worked hard for!"],[2552,2615,"While you're playing"],[2615,2715,"the devoted husband,"],[2719,2815,"your precious wife"],[2831,2994,"is forcing me to be a janitor!"],[3299,3524,"I don't give a damn if she's forcing you"],[3524,3645,"to cut off your fingers."],[3716,3974,"I need Emily to sign her shares to me."],[4024,4225,"If she suspects I'm unfaithful,"],[4245,4379,"she will tear those shares up"],[4391,4546,"and we get nothing."],[4633,4700,"Is that what you want?"],[4783,4925,"Save the lecture, Robert."],[4984,5125,"I want what we agreed on."],[5221,5276,"The company"],[5301,5376,"and your signature"],[5376,5497,"on those divorce papers."],[5568,5638,"I won't play"],[5638,5764,"the other woman forever."],[5780,5809,"Good."],[6031,6056,"Now,"],[6218,6306,"keep playing janitor."],[6452,6535,"Make Emily happy,"],[6569,6706,"or neither of us get what we want."],[6823,6881,"Perfect."],[6931,7048,"I wonder how the board members"],[7048,7178,"will react to this."]],"54":[[387,425,"Sorry."],[492,604,"Are you kidding me?"],[671,709,"Fuck!"],[763,809,"Stacy,"],[905,1055,"do you mind picking up my dry cleaning?"],[1071,1134,"I need something nice to wear"],[1134,1284,"for the shareholders banquet tomorrow."],[1330,1388,"But I, I'm..."],[1589,1651,"Go do it now."],[1801,1843,"No!"],[2406,2460,"Hi, how are you?"],[2494,2527,"Hi."],[2644,2702,"I'm here to pick up"],[2702,2827,"Mrs. Stewart's dry cleaning."],[2861,2940,"Okay, I'll be right back."],[3620,3645,"Yep."],[8487,8604,"Good luck finding something"],[8604,8675,"to wear tomorrow,"],[8679,8883,"you manipulative little skank!"]],"55":[[487,538,"Stacy,"],[571,633,"perfect timing."],[1009,1071,"There was an incident"],[1080,1172,"at the dry cleaner."],[1209,1409,"Some worker spilled bleach"],[1409,1493,"and dropped their lunch"],[1497,1609,"all over your clothes."],[1622,1776,"Huh, complete disaster!"],[2293,2352,"Interesting."],[2627,2719,"That exact same thing"],[2727,2811,"seems to have happened"],[2811,2940,"in my own dresser as well."],[3044,3078,"Hmm,"],[3157,3274,"must be one of the maids."],[3357,3470,"Using bleach and eating lunch"],[3478,3574,"at the same time."],[3674,3778,"These people can't be trusted"],[3782,3941,"to do anything nice."],[4008,4091,"It's alright, Stacy."],[4154,4229,"Accidents happen."],[4375,4462,"Thankfully I have a dress"],[4462,4579,"in the back of my closet"],[4617,4754,"and today's the perfect day"],[4763,4808,"to wear it."],[6956,7023,"That dress,"],[7098,7194,"it looks familiar."],[7374,7453,"Emily, that"],[7632,7724,"dress you're wearing..."],[7782,7966,"Do you not recognize it?"],[8145,8254,"It's the dress my mom wore"],[8254,8329,"the day she died."]],"56":[[604,696,"You seem nervous."],[763,838,"Is there something wrong?"],[1034,1063,"No,"],[1209,1255,"not at all."],[1568,1634,"It's just that,"],[1668,1776,"see, people might talk."],[1964,2043,"Wearing that dress"],[2043,2260,"to a shareholders banquet,"],[2318,2360,"you know,"],[2381,2523,"isn't exactly appropriate."],[2915,3019,"When my parents died,"],[3073,3224,"they left me a company to protect"],[3240,3357,"and a legacy to uphold."],[3549,3649,"This dress is a reminder"],[3649,3762,"of that responsibility."],[3920,3970,"Besides,"],[4045,4195,"some occasions call for a reminder"],[4195,4295,"of what we once lost,"],[4304,4337,"am I right?"],[4608,4650,"Let's go."],[4783,4854,"The car's waiting."],[5563,5689,"Mom, Dad,"],[5764,5960,"today's the day I make them pay."],[6018,6310,"The day I show them exactly"],[6348,6443,"who they're dealing with."],[7311,7465,"Brian, I hope you're safe."],[7511,7665,"I'm going to finish what we started."],[8692,8750,"Time to move."],[9113,9205,"Emily, hold on."],[9242,9313,"I'm on my way."],[9517,9572,"Going somewhere?"]],"57":[[54,137,"Here's a toast"],[137,275,"to Stewart Corporation's"],[291,425,"rightful new leader."],[442,508,"About time."],[538,646,"Emily had no business"],[646,729,"being the CEO."],[779,850,"Deaf CEO,"],[884,967,"with a criminal brother."],[1088,1134,"What a joke."],[1146,1230,"Gentlemen, please."],[1313,1405,"She's still my wife."],[1459,1509,"For now."],[1551,1664,"Speaking of wives,"],[1664,1705,"Robert,"],[1751,1847,"my sister Jessica"],[1847,1981,"has been asking about you."],[2056,2268,"She would be a perfect match."],[2327,2435,"Imagine a woman"],[2435,2540,"who could actually hear"],[2540,2669,"when she's being spoken to."],[2836,2969,"Not to be outdone, Robert,"],[2969,3098,"but my cousin Sarah's"],[3098,3215,"a Yale graduate."],[3315,3411,"Must be humiliating"],[3411,3611,"dragging around a deaf woman"],[3611,3695,"to every function."],[3716,3774,"Though I suppose"],[3774,3874,"there's one benefit."],[3962,4091,"You can insult her behind her back"],[4091,4225,"and she can't hear a damn thing."],[4550,4650,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[4700,4771,"please welcome"],[4771,4971,"the CEO of Stewart Corporation,"],[5009,5138,"Mrs. Emily Stewart."],[6101,6247,"That's the dress her mother died in."],[6293,6393,"She's literally wearing"],[6402,6506,"a dead woman's clothes."],[6519,6585,"Stay away from her."],[6585,6715,"She's clearly not right in the head."],[6731,6840,"No wonder her husband is"],[6840,6956,"taking over the company."],[8195,8270,"Before we begin,"],[8283,8362,"I think there's something"],[8362,8529,"you all should know about my husband."],[8621,8712,"And what he's done"],[8837,8908,"for our family."]],"58":[[212,296,"My husband,"],[333,425,"Robert Matthews,"],[425,529,"has made tremendous"],[529,629,"commitment to this company"],[629,750,"that no one knows about."],[880,934,"Robert has been"],[934,1071,"more than a partner in life."],[1405,1547,"His commitment to this company"],[1614,1697,"is absolute"],[1851,1947,"and instrumental"],[2097,2235,"in developing relationships"],[2235,2331,"that have helped us grow."],[2544,2619,"Looks like everything's"],[2619,2727,"falling into place."],[3795,3970,"Sneaking away from your deaf bride"],[3970,4087,"to fuck her stepsister"],[4087,4195,"on your anniversary?"],[4254,4379,"You're such a bad husband."],[4466,4546,"Why waste my time"],[4546,4658,"with a worthless bitch"],[4717,4833,"when I can have a real woman?"],[5568,5705,"I need Emily"],[5705,5855,"to sign those shares to me."],[5935,6135,"If she suspects I'm unfaithful,"],[6160,6293,"she will tear those shares up"],[6306,6452,"and we get nothing."],[7052,7236,"Your downfall begins now, Robert."]],"59":[[296,333,"Emily,"],[383,433,"please."],[542,625,"This isn't what it looks like."],[625,704,"You have to believe me."],[1201,1259,"Believe you?"],[1409,1497,"Like how I believed that"],[1497,1639,"when you said you loved me?"],[1818,1856,"That woman"],[1864,1956,"that you cheated on me with"],[1956,2110,"is my stepsister, Robert!"],[2114,2152,"Emily,"],[2243,2281,"please."],[2289,2414,"I trusted you with my heart."],[2569,2619,"I trusted you"],[2619,2748,"with my family's company,"],[2831,2927,"everything!"],[3065,3232,"And you were just waiting"],[3232,3349,"to rip it all away from me!"],[3520,3636,"Emily, please,"],[3737,3803,"forgive Robert."],[3903,3962,"That boy"],[4041,4137,"doesn't know any better."],[4270,4337,"Forgive him?"],[4542,4654,"After what I just saw?"],[4792,4842,"I was just"],[4963,5130,"testing Stacy's loyalty to you"],[5188,5326,"to make sure she wouldn't betray you."],[5530,5655,"You expect me to believe that?"],[6452,6656,"You will sign these shares to me."],[6715,6765,"Right now."],[6986,7027,"Sign it,"],[7057,7098,"Emily."],[7207,7374,"I won't ask again!"],[7515,7645,"Get away from my sister."]],"60":[[158,287,"What the hell is he doing here?"],[404,513,"He was..."],[550,596,"Locked up?"],[667,750,"Is that what you were going to say,"],[763,800,"Thomas?"],[875,1051,"Don't trust these two, everyone!"],[1121,1234,"They've been conspiring together"],[1234,1330,"to take over the company"],[1330,1463,"since the very beginning!"],[1526,1643,"And why should we believe you?"],[1697,1730,"You're the one"],[1730,1856,"who transferred our company's"],[1856,2014,"emergency funds overseas."],[2035,2223,"You nearly bankrupted us."],[2273,2389,"We've seen the transfer papers"],[2389,2494,"with your signature."],[2531,2669,"The documents were forged."],[2736,2861,"Thomas was kicked out of the company"],[2873,2919,"years ago"],[2919,3032,"for embezzling millions."],[3128,3169,"You don't think"],[3169,3340,"he'd know how to forge documents?"],[3528,3695,"I didn't forge those documents."],[3820,3933,"This man is clearly lying!"],[4149,4212,"Then you won't mind"],[4212,4287,"having these examined"],[4287,4354,"by experts"],[4379,4421,"right now."],[4529,4608,"Let's see what they have to say."],[4729,4829,"You have no idea"],[4929,5009,"who you're messing with."],[5075,5142,"Is this true?"],[5213,5317,"He's lying, right?"],[5492,5568,"Mr. Henderson?"],[5626,5693,"Say something!"]],"61":[[50,125,"Say something!"],[358,442,"You have no shame."],[525,696,"You cheated on me with my stepsister"],[696,838,"and you framed my brother"],[888,921,"and you-"],[934,1142,"What do you expect?"],[1276,1322,"You're lucky"],[1322,1459,"I'm even willing to touch"],[1468,1559,"a deaf freak like you."],[1760,1847,"Do you guys have any idea"],[1847,1901,"what it's like"],[1922,2047,"living with someone like this?"],[2122,2243,"I just want a real woman."],[2389,2452,"Who can hear me."],[2619,2694,"Who can please me."],[2761,2831,"This is true."],[2927,3123,"She may be smart and rich,"],[3174,3324,"but she's still defective."],[3365,3541,"Yeah, it's not Robert's fault."],[3603,3762,"Emily's the one dragging him down."],[4004,4041,"Hear that?"],[4179,4254,"They're on my side."],[4425,4471,"Oh wait."],[4512,4529,"No."],[4629,4804,"You can't hear them,"],[4867,4917,"can you?"],[5263,5417,"Maybe if you ask me nicely,"],[5509,5601,"I'll repeat myself."],[5676,5922,"Just like this."],[6335,6427,"Actually, Robert,"],[6652,6781,"I can hear you perfectly fine."]],"62":[[62,229,"In fact, I've heard everything."],[337,429,"I have heard every time"],[429,563,"you had sex with Stacy"],[563,759,"in the room next to our bedroom."],[913,1172,"I heard every ploy against my family."],[1288,1543,"Every whisper, every lie."],[1705,1776,"I heard"],[1964,2047,"everything."],[2147,2177,"No,"],[2310,2406,"that's impossible."],[2544,2594,"You're deaf."],[2765,2848,"I regained my hearing"],[2848,2982,"on our third year anniversary."],[3174,3303,"You thought my silence"],[3390,3482,"was a weakness,"],[3803,3920,"but it was my secret weapon"],[4041,4120,"to survive,"],[4137,4266,"to protect my company"],[4304,4387,"and my family."],[4637,4679,"And now,"],[4884,5030,"now I'll make sure you never take"],[5030,5075,"what's something"],[5075,5209,"that you cannot have!"]],"63":[[141,183,"Emily,"],[183,287,"no, you see, um,"],[350,487,"you're confused."],[546,817,"Every, everything that I have done for you"],[934,1042,"was for, for us."],[1126,1213,"Okay, for both of us."],[1213,1280,"I love you."],[1689,1739,"Love me."],[1931,2002,"You know, there was a time"],[2002,2102,"I would have believed that."],[2214,2377,"And then you slept with my stepsister."],[2581,2744,"And that was the tip of the iceberg."],[3003,3140,"You all think that my parents died"],[3140,3215,"in a car crash,"],[3215,3319,"but here's the truth."],[3470,3636,"Robert and Thomas tampered"],[3636,3749,"with the brakes on their car"],[3820,3958,"and murdered them in cold blood."],[4312,4375,"She's lying."],[4437,4533,"There, there's no proof."],[4575,4675,"Oh, but there is."],[4763,4879,"I have a recording of you"],[4879,5046,"confessing to killing our parents"],[5096,5246,"with Thomas' help."]],"64":[[538,638,"Looking for something, Brian?"],[809,855,"Perhaps"],[921,1017,"a recording device?"],[1443,1530,"Emily, hold on."],[1568,1647,"I'm on my way."],[1768,1826,"Going somewhere?"],[2369,2506,"Robert and I have worked too hard"],[2515,2573,"for this day."],[2619,2786,"And I'm not going to let you ruin it."],[2827,2886,"Take him somewhere"],[2886,2961,"he can't escape."],[4099,4200,"You think you've got me,"],[4200,4237,"Brian?"],[4692,4725,"See?"],[4808,4871,"No evidence."],[4950,5109,"Just empty accusations."],[5130,5246,"How dare you accuse"],[5246,5476,"two respected executives like this!"],[5513,5618,"The Stewarts are"],[5659,5784,"desperate to take the company."],[5847,5918,"They'd say anything."],[6022,6101,"You've been lying"],[6101,6193,"about your condition."],[6231,6356,"Why should we believe you now?"],[6627,6748,"Looks like you've lost, Emily."]],"65":[[70,154,"Oh, but Robert,"],[254,350,"we've only just begun."],[1076,1167,"Wait, is that?"],[1280,1384,"The recording device"],[1384,1476,"that Brian used"],[1476,1647,"to record Robert's confession?"],[1710,1747,"Yes."],[1780,1860,"It's not possible."],[2006,2077,"I destroyed it."],[2168,2243,"Destroyed it?"],[2590,2673,"How's my brother doing?"],[2723,2769,"He's fine."],[2815,2915,"But he wanted me to give you this."],[3795,3862,"Has everything you need"],[3862,3903,"to take down"],[3903,3991,"Thomas and Robert."],[4049,4133,"He's staying in a warehouse"],[4133,4200,"for your safety."],[4320,4391,"And he'll make his move"],[4400,4458,"once the shareholder"],[4458,4529,"meeting starts."],[4750,4792,"Thank you."],[5000,5134,"That was a worthless decoy."],[5309,5351,"The evidence"],[5351,5459,"has been in my possession"],[5488,5551,"all along,"],[5847,5951,"just waiting for me"],[6047,6110,"to use it"],[6147,6293,"in this moment."]],"66":[[212,471,"Thomas has been plotting his revenge"],[471,629,"since the day your parents kicked him"],[629,717,"out of Stewart Corp"],[717,834,"for embezzling millions."],[867,1005,"He came to me with a plan"],[1013,1101,"to get rid of them"],[1151,1234,"once and for all."],[1267,1309,"And,"],[1368,1443,"let me tell you,"],[1518,1622,"watching that car"],[1655,1810,"go right over the cliff,"],[1922,1997,"that was something."],[2022,2118,"You son of a bitch."],[2118,2202,"You fucking killed them!"],[2231,2331,"You fucking monster!"],[2344,2369,"Yeah."],[2406,2427,"Well,"],[2435,2560,"you and Emily are gonna join them."],[3078,3132,"Idiot!"],[3303,3420,"You ruined everything!"],[3557,3599,"Robert."],[3691,3766,"It's over!"],[3908,3999,"It's over, Stacy."],[4079,4133,"Everything that"],[4137,4229,"we've worked hard for"],[4241,4346,"is ruined!"]],"67":[[196,241,"That's the girl"],[250,375,"Robert cheated on Emily with."],[400,462,"That skank"],[487,583,"betrayed her stepsister"],[583,696,"and thinks she can get away with it?"],[696,863,"She's not just a home wrecker,"],[892,1026,"she's sleeping with a murderer."],[1376,1497,"You murderers!"],[1676,1739,"Oh, no."],[1764,1789,"No."],[2002,2072,"Come on, you're under arrest,"],[2072,2160,"buddy, come on."],[2160,2243,"It's over, Robert."],[2502,2635,"You'll be signing the divorce papers"],[2635,2690,"soon enough."],[2952,3078,"You stupid bitch."],[3090,3169,"You'll regret this."],[3269,3307,"And you,"],[3461,3536,"I only kept you around"],[3536,3641,"because you were too stupid"],[3641,3762,"to realize I was using you."],[3828,3953,"You couldn't even help me finish off"],[3962,4054,"one deaf bitch."]],"68":[[312,358,"Mhm."],[496,529,"Yes,"],[529,633,"there will be some changes made"],[633,825,"to Stewart Corporations."],[934,1001,"Robert?"],[1422,1505,"What are you doing here?"],[1605,1810,"Stacy bailed me out"],[1810,1935,"with all the money I had left."],[1997,2118,"Turns out she's actually good"],[2118,2239,"for something after all."],[2527,2560,"Here's the deal."],[2706,2773,"50 million,"],[2911,3032,"and I'll sign the divorce paper."],[3144,3415,"Or I'll just drag it out for years."],[3582,3712,"I don't respond to threats."],[3853,4070,"If you had any kind of decency,"],[4133,4266,"I might've been generous,"],[4362,4525,"but you showed me your true colors."],[4662,4696,"Oh,"],[4738,4767,"I'm sorry,"],[4767,4892,"actually, it sounds like"],[4892,5005,"you're probably still deaf"],[5005,5121,"because you didn't hear"],[5121,5192,"what I just said."],[5321,5534,"50 million for a clean divorce..."],[6089,6168,"No one gets hurt."]],"69":[[58,145,"Get away from her!"],[325,358,"Oh."],[462,517,"Stacy,"],[596,696,"make yourself useful."],[825,875,"Tie him up."],[992,1138,"He can watch as I kill his sister"],[1180,1272,"right in front of his eyes."],[1918,1968,"God!"],[2506,2602,"You stupid bitch!"],[2615,2719,"You betrayed me!"],[2769,2911,"I wanted a rich husband,"],[2932,3036,"not prison time."],[3115,3203,"I'll cut my losses"],[3203,3353,"and find someone else."],[3453,3557,"Why would I go down with you?"],[3720,3841,"I did a good job, didn't I?"]],"70":[[200,266,"Yes, you did."],[417,538,"Thank you for giving us a warning"],[538,604,"ahead of time."],[905,1042,"Sign the divorce papers"],[1042,1105,"now! - God."],[3023,3065,"Please,"],[3153,3274,"it was all a mistake, okay?"],[3349,3415,"I made a mistake,"],[3415,3453,"Emily!"],[3528,3616,"Emily, you can hear me!"],[3636,3666,"Sorry,"],[3666,3757,"I can't hear you. - Come on!"],[3757,3849,"I know you can hear me."],[3849,3970,"God, don't play that game!"],[4300,4379,"You're under arrest ma'am."],[4400,4437,"Hey!"],[4679,4713,"Ma'am,"],[4742,4838,"what would you like me to do with her?"]],"71":[[95,137,"Let her go."],[254,300,"What?"],[358,450,"She helped us,"],[538,671,"and she saved my life today."],[880,1009,"Her punishment will come one day."],[1142,1222,"Thank you, Emily."],[2552,2594,"We did it."],[2627,2669,"No,"],[2761,2902,"you did it, sis."],[3707,3912,"Well, that concludes my report"],[3912,3995,"on my six months"],[3995,4237,"as CEO of Stewart Corporation,"],[4291,4387,"with our new direction"],[4391,4650,"and with Brian as our returning COO."],[4729,4871,"We have not only recovered"],[4871,4979,"our emergency funds,"],[4988,5084,"but we've also exceeded"],[5084,5184,"our all projections."],[5242,5501,"150 percent growth in just two quarters."],[5530,5647,"I believe our parents would call that"],[5647,5784,"a successful comeback."],[6218,6414,"Such remarkable leadership."],[6439,6539,"The Stewarts have really"],[6539,6664,"turned this company around."],[6698,6806,"The company has never been"],[6806,6886,"in better hands."],[7319,7403,"Who would have thought that"],[7428,7524,"six months ago,"],[7524,7682,"we were fighting for our lives,"],[7682,7795,"and now you're CEO"],[7795,7907,"and I'm back as COO."],[7962,8003,"Yeah, well,"],[8012,8095,"justice always has a way"],[8095,8183,"of setting things right."],[8229,8283,"Oh, absolutely."],[8337,8416,"Got a surprise for you."]],"72":[[16,100,"Got a surprise for you."],[246,316,"Your divorce from Robert"],[316,429,"has been finalized."],[525,629,"Oh, finally."],[729,859,"How are the troubled trio"],[867,921,"doing anyway?"],[1005,1038,"Well,"],[1113,1230,"25 to life for Robert,"],[1230,1297,"and Thomas."],[1297,1363,"And Stacy,"],[1472,1505,"well,"],[1568,1626,"she's working"],[1626,1714,"at the same dry cleaners"],[1714,1835,"that she destroyed my clothes at."],[1835,2010,"So that's poetic justice,"],[2010,2056,"I'll say."],[2072,2097,"Well,"],[2156,2273,"this calls for a celebration."],[2327,2385,"Yeah?"],[2769,2844,"To justice."],[2957,3003,"To family."],[3699,3791,"We did it, Mom and Dad."],[3941,3999,"The company's back"],[3999,4066,"where it belongs."],[4099,4175,"Who would have thought"],[4175,4300,"that your deafness"],[4300,4333,"would end up"],[4333,4454,"being your greatest strength?"],[4575,4608,"Yeah, well,"],[4608,4733,"sometimes it pays to listen"],[4733,4829,"more than you speak."],[5017,5050,"Yeah."],[5142,5188,"So,"],[5276,5305,"dinner?"],[5422,5563,"I got us a reservation"],[5563,5655,"at a restaurant downtown."],[5663,5722,"Sorry, what?"],[5722,5822,"I, I didn't hear you."],[6089,6168,"Very funny."],[6360,6435,"Yeah, yeah."]]}